data.text:
@chamirafernando @chamirafernando Hi, I am sorry to hear your bags were damaged. To report the damage on your other bag, you need return to the airport and arrange that via the Baggage Service.
You can read more about the process here https://t.co/yaDBpcxdM2
Kind regards, Mikael.

@dorothyapl Hi! 
I am sorry to hear that. If your baggage weighs 23–32 kg or exceeds the standard size of 158 cm (length + width + height), you will be charged a flat rate fee and the fee can only be paid at the airport. You can find more info here https://t.co/5Fv72Ic374 

//Farah

@ca2111111 Hi, I am sorry to hear your bag is delayed. If you haven't reported your bag at the airport, please do so here: https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3 You can track your bag here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU
or call baggage service here: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2
Kind regards, Lena

@AshokSh82920275 Hi @AshokSh82920275!
I recommend you to contact the Travel agency where you bought the tickets. Since you have provided your booking reference, I also recommend you delete this tweet.
Kind regards, Lena

@damiandugdale Hi @damiandugdale!
Our customer service has a processing time of approximately 6 to 8 weeks.
Kind regards, Lena

@TomBreckwoldt1 You can apply for a refund for the new suitcase here: https://t.co/zItZlSXhJp 
However, I cannot guarantee that it will be refunded as these claims are handled by Customer Care on a case-to-case basis. 
Kind Regards, Natasha

@dansouleles Hello
You make your claim via this webform https://t.co/cXegpq56aG , google chrome usually works good as browser with this form.
Kind regards /Anna

@myXP Hello, we are unfortunately not able to look into individual cases from Twitter. For information about your case please contact us on live chat or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@DaKaCmbs @DaKaCmbs Hi, I'm sorry to hear that.  You can read about damaged baggage and how to proceed with your case on our website 
https://t.co/yaDBpcxdM2
Kind regards, Mikael.

@kpop_verse1 Hi!
I can tell you have reported the bag missing and are following the process continuously. I therefore recommend you to contact Baggage Service to receive further information and updates regarding your missing bag from here: https://t.co/We1FdD7ZiM
Best regards, Angelica

@JessFloyd Hi @JessFloyd, transportation of animals in cabin and as checked baggage is forbidden to/from UK. It must be sent as cargo. 
The following service animals, SVAN, are permitted in the cabin - Seeing eye, Hearing aid, Diabetic aid and Seizure aid.
Kind regards, Mikael.

@Lily_Lifa Hello, I'm sorry to hear that the call was disconnected. Please try calling us again, or contact us on live chat and we can help you take a look at the cancelled flight https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@OneDizzyPenguin Hello, I recommend you to try to use the seat selector again a bit later to see if it works better, or you can contact us on live chat/phone for help with requesting the seat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@Bigtunaheyohhh Hello, I'm sorry to hear that your flight was cancelled. Please contact us on live chat or phone and we can help you take a look at other alternatives https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@SailorWinner Hello, please contact us on live chat with your booking reference and we can help you take a look at the seats https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@field_trips_ Hello, I'm sorry to hear that your baggage is missing. Since it has been more than 21 days since the baggage was lost, I recommend you to submit a compensation claim for lost baggage at https://t.co/zItZlSXhJp

Best regards,
Anton.

@davie_mcd Hello, please contact us on live chat or phone with your EuroBonus number and we can help you order the EuroBonus card and luggage tags https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@puritongav Hi @puritongav I'm sorry to hear your bike is delayed. I can't check the status in my system, you need to contact the baggage service at the airport for more info https://t.co/ZV9bTNLSZs
You can read about delayed baggage here: https://t.co/yaDBpcOODA
Kind regards, Mikael

@monicacsango Hej, prova gärna att tömma cache och cookies i din webbläsare och säkerställ att du inte har någon VPN aktiverad på ditt nätverk för att se om det hjälper.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@MT24548928 Hello, please contact us on live chat and we can help you with this, during office hours you will have the ability to chat with a live agent, outside of office hours our robot Turi can assist with more simpler errands https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@Froebelbanjo Hello, please contact us on live chat and we can help you rebook the flight ticket(s) https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@missjtahir Hello, I'm sorry to hear that your baggage is delayed. If you haven't already reported the baggage as delayed, please do so at https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3 - you can also call baggage service for help https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2

Best regards,
Anton.

@Ell13484176N Hi, our Customer Care department which handles claims and general feedback is not able to assist with EuroBonus matters so I recommend you to contact us on chat or phone instead for help with your retroactive claim of points https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@captchaostheory Hi, I am sorry to hear that the luggage is delayed. We are not able to assist with these cases over social media so I will have to kindly ask that you call our baggage service support for help https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2

Best regards,
Anton.

@s_u_n_i_l_v Hi. In that case you need to call baggage service for more information about where the baggage is located. We don't have any insight into these cases from here unfortunately.

Best regards,
Anton.

@s_u_n_i_l_v Hello, if you have the file reference for your delayed baggage case (for example OSLSK12345) you can use this reference to track the case yourself at https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU - If not I must kindly ask that you try and call baggage service again later.

Best regards,
Anton.

@vanScherrenburg Hello
The chat is open again tomorrow 07:00 - 19:00 ( Scandinavian time ).
Kind regards /Anna

@Sweet_n_Swedish Hi Booz Weg
Here is a contact list for lost luggage I hope that helps https://t.co/We1FdD7ZiM you can also check the webpage for the airport if they have any contact for lost luggage.
Kind regards /Anna

@kieransimpson Hi Kieran 
Contact our customer support via chat or phone and we will look into it https://t.co/fxd6BsEJUx our chat open 07:00 scandinavian time.
Kind regards /Anna

@vanScherrenburg Hello, we are unfortunately not able to assist with individual cases over Twitter. Please contact us on live chat or phone and we can help you look into this https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.
